.. |rk_soc| replace:: RK3576

.. |RAM| replace:: 4GB LPDDR5

.. |eMMC| replace:: 64GB

.. |disp_des| replace:: |dispsize| ten-point capacitive touch screen with a resolution of |res| pixels and a brightness of |bright|

.. |disp_table_des| replace:: |dispsize| LCD, |res|, High Brightness: |bright|

.. |mounting_table| replace:: Panel, VESA

.. |uart_des| replace:: This product has 4 x UART by default, 6 x UART channels at most. The default configuration is 2 x RS232 and 2 x RS485, including 1 RS232 debug port. The 2 x CAN FD can be configured to RS232.

.. |m2_spec| replace:: Optional, supports M.2 M-Key 2230/2242/2260/2280 NVME SSD (PCI-E 3.0 x1)

.. |tscreen| replace:: 10-point capacitive touch screen

.. |HDMI_des| replace:: 1 x HDMI OUT

.. |USB| replace:: 1 x USB 2.0 HOST, 1 x USB 3.0 HOST, 1 x USB Type-C

.. |USB_conflict| replace:: USB3.0 port and USB-C port cannot be used at the same time

.. |usb_usbc_conflict| replace:: The USB3.0 type-A host and USB-C **can't be used** at the same time. Before boot into OS, USB-C is enabled for installing OS image; after boot into OS, USB-A is enabled but USB-C is disabled. |br| In Android, these can be configured, USB3.0 type A is enabled by default, but you can switch to using USB-C in the software for debugging; in Linux, these can't be configured.

.. |LAN| replace:: 1 x RJ45, GbE

.. |LAN_des| replace:: 1 x RJ45

.. |npu| replace:: 6 TOPS(Sparsity)@INT8

.. |poe| replace:: Optional, Power Over Ethernet 802.3af/at

.. |GPIO| replace:: 8 Channels Isolated IO, 4 x Input and 4 x Output

.. |gpio_conn| replace:: **phoenix connector**

.. |opt1_4g| replace:: Supported, Optional

.. |opt2_wifibt| replace:: Integrated WiFi/BT Module

.. |vin_rng| replace:: From 15V to 30V

.. |rs232| replace:: Default to 2 x RS232 (including 1 debug port). Up to 6 x RS232.

.. |rs485| replace:: Default to 2 x RS485. Optionally, these 2 x RS485 can be configured to RS232.

.. |can| replace:: Default to 2 x CAN FD. Optionally, these 2 x CAN FD can be configured to RS232.

.. |vesa_screws| replace:: **100 x 100** mm, 4 x **M4** (6mm)

.. |rtc| replace:: High accuracy RTC with farad capacitor, can work 1 week after power off **(default)**. High accuracy RTC with lithium coin battery, can work 3 years after power off *(optional)*.

.. |buzzer| replace:: Yes

.. |audio| replace:: 3.5mm Audio In/Out Connector, 2W Internal Speaker

.. |storage| replace:: TF Card, Supports up to 128GB SDHC